        <h3>Dressed by the kids Day</h3>
        <label style="margin: 20px auto;">08 March, 2020</label>
        <p class="ptext1">Oxfam’s annual Dressed by the Kids Day is a fun event for everyone who doesn’t take themselves too seriously. Sure, you risk looking like a fool for a day (in fact, that’s what anyone who sponsors you to take part will be hoping for). But for once you won’t have to worry about what to wear, and the kids will enjoy abusing their power over your wardrobe while you enjoy raising awareness of sustainable fashion to battle poverty.
        </p>
